messages.message: Have we considered adding tags or being able to re-name or organise app runs? A customer pointed out today he couldn't figure out which run was from which test and he wanted me to feed this back

not aware of anything existing - created a new ticket to track this. I'd suggest using a combination of development workspaces & distinct deployments to track testing for now. If they're using the API or outbound integrations, those should provide the runIDs too, but would need to be tracked offline.
